title=Exclusive Interview: Zac Efron and Richard Linklater on ME AND ORSON WELLES; Plus Zac Addresses DEATH NOTE Rumors|last=Weintraub|first=Steve|date=2009-11-22|accessdate=2016-04-10|publisher=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|archive-date=2020-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200109234739/https://collider.com/exclusive-interview-zac-efron-and-richard-linklater-on-me-and-orson-welles-plus-zac-addresses-death-note-rumors/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年1月13日，透露[[沙恩·布萊克|沙恩·布萊克]]曾受聘請執導電影，而劇本由安東尼·巴格羅茲和查爾斯·蒙德里撰寫<ref>{{cite news |url = http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/warner-bros-taps-shane-black-for-japanese-manga-death-note/ |title = Warner Bros Taps Shane Black For Japanese Manga 'Death Note' |last = Fleming |first = Mike Jr |accessdate = 2011-01-14 |date = 2011-01-13 |publisher = [[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]] |archive-date = 2011-07-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110717055040/http://www.deadline.com/2011/01/warner-bros-taps-shane-black-for-japanese-manga-death-note/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。華納兄弟計劃改變背景故事，主角[[夜神月|夜神月]]使用筆記本是為了復仇而不是為了實現正義，並在故事中刪除[[死亡筆記角色列表#死神|死神]]。布萊克反對此改變<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-11-02/shane-black-describes-changes-he-opposed-to-warner-death-note/|title=Shane Black Describes Changes He Opposed to Warner's Death Note|last=Loo|first=Egan|date=2011-11-02|accessdate=2016-04-10|publisher=Anime News Network|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117191514/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/interest/2011-11-02/shane-black-describes-changes-he-opposed-to-warner-death-note|dead-url=no}}</ref>。布萊克於2013年受{{link-en|Bleeding Cool|Bleeding Cool}}網站採訪時，證實自己仍打算執導電影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/04/24/shane-black-on-his-death-note-and-doc-savage-movies/?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter|title=Shane Black On His Death Note And Doc Savage Movies|last=Connelly|first=Brendon|date=2013-04-24|accessdate=2016-04-10|work=[[Bleeding_Cool|Bleeding Cool]]|archive-date=2014-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140201221511/http://www.bleedingcool.com/2013/04/24/shane-black-on-his-death-note-and-doc-savage-movies/?utm_source=dlvr.it&utm_medium=twitter|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。2014年7月，又傳出[[葛斯·范·桑|葛斯·范·桑]]取代布萊克擔任導演，而羅伊·李、道格·戴維森、林暐和布萊恩·維騰繼續擔任監製，並由Lin Pictures和眩暈娛樂製作<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.tracking-board.com/tb-exclusive-gus-van-sant-takes-over-death-note/|title={TB EXCLUSIVE} Gus Van Sant Takes Over “Death Note”|last=Whitehead|first=Donna|work=The Tracking Board|date=2014-07-10|accessdate=2014-07-10}}</ref>。

